# Refactoring and Optimization Rules

## For AI Agent

### Refactoring Principles

- Refactor incrementally - make small, safe changes
- Maintain existing functionality while improving code quality
- Run tests after each refactoring step to ensure nothing breaks
- Extract common patterns into reusable utilities
- Improve code readability without changing behavior
- Remove dead code and unused imports

### Optimization Guidelines

- Profile before optimizing - identify actual bottlenecks
- Optimize reconciliation logic for VNode tree updates
- Use memoization strategically (useMemo, useCallback, memo HOC)
- Minimize DOM operations by batching updates

### Refactoring Checklist

- [ ] All existing tests pass
- [ ] No new linter errors introduced
- [ ] Type safety maintained or improved
- [ ] Code is more maintainable

